Important:
----------

You have to make the following changes in the glfw.h file:

Replace:

 #include <OpenGL/gl.h>
 #ifndef GLFW_NO_GLU
  #include <OpenGL/glu.h>
 #endif
 
with:
 
 #ifdef GLFW_GL3
  #include <OpenGL/gl3.h>
 #else
  #include <OpenGL/gl.h>
  #ifndef GLFW_NO_GLU
   #include <OpenGL/glu.h>
  #endif
 #endif
 
This allows you to switch between OpenGL 3 and the older version of OpenGL.
 